| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2995 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d0fb4134-3f62-52a6-9f1b-c74a6a300784"
